# Parametros API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear parametro (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "examenId": 2,
  "code": "P001",
  "name": "Hemoglobina",
  "unit": "g/dL",
  "refMin": 12.0,
  "refMax": 17.0,
  "typeValue": "NUMERICO",
  "decimals": 2,
  "visualOrder": 1,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar parametros (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/parametros/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener parametro por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar parametro (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "mg/dL",
  "refMin": 11.5,
  "refMax": 16.5,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar parametro fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1/public

### Baja logica de parametro (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear parametro (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "examenId": 3,
  "code": "P010",
  "name": "Glucosa",
  "unit": "mg/dL",
  "refMin": 70,
  "refMax": 110,
  "typeValue": "NUMERICO",
  "decimals": 1,
  "visualOrder": 2,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar parametros (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/parametros
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener parametro por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar parametro (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "mmol/L",
  "refMin": 4.0,
  "refMax": 6.0,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar parametro fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de parametro (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/parametro/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
